<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Your Referral Reward</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 24px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background-color: #eef4ff;
        color: #3758f9;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .code {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono',
          'Courier New', monospace;
        background: #111827;
        color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 16px;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="badge">Referral Reward</div>
      <h2>Hi {{name}}, you earned a coupon! ðŸŽ‰</h2>
      <p>
        Thanks for inviting your friends to SOSTECH Store. You&apos;ve reached a
        referral milestone with <strong>{{referralCount}}</strong> completed
        referral(s).
      </p>

      <p>
        Here is your reward coupon worth
        <strong>{{discountPercent}}% off</strong> on your next order:
      </p>

      <div class="code">{{couponCode}}</div>

      <p>
        This coupon is <strong>single-use</strong>, linked to your account, and
        valid until <strong>{{expiresAt}}</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Just apply this code at checkout on your next purchase. No need to
        claim anything else.
      </p>

      <p class="footer">
        If you didn&apos;t expect this email, you can safely ignore it.<br />
        &copy; {{currentYear}} SOSTECH Store. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
  </html>

